commit.message: Added parameters for grid size & resolution
Display URL used to download map
Clean up code & test distance cubed with weight squared
Fixed issues caused when upscaling the resolution
Fix for canvas not being cleared between requests
Fixed args for size and tap counts
Taps are now displayed in bigger circles and houses have transparency
Changed algorithm to used to detect houses. Removed redundant code in recolour.py
